    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this absolute stunner. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one, and it's in truly perfect shape\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. It\u2019s an absolute dream to drive and I'm only letting it go because I'm downsizing. Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
