    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its flawless factory paint and high-gloss finish. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with premium leather upholstery that shows zero signs of wear and still retains that new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians using original parts. With incredibly low mileage and a comprehensive service history, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection. It is, quite simply, the finest example of its kind available on the market today.",
      "price": 48900.0,
