    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen exhibits an impeccable aesthetic profile and mechanical integrity that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a legacy of meticulous stewardship. We invite the discerning driver to acquire a motorcar that transcends the typical pre-owned market in both condition and performance.",
