    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014I've babied it since day one! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. You won't find a single scratch on it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why I'm so proud of this one. It's the perfect upgrade you've been waiting for! \u2728",
