    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This A80 chassis represents a rare opportunity to own a preserved icon of Japanese engineering. At its heart lies the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, featuring its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and factory-sealed internals. The drivetrain is anchored by the coveted Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every mechanical interface, from the double-wishbone suspension bushings to the hydraulic steering rack, remains tight and responsive, reflecting a vehicle that has been maintained with clinical precision. Free from aftermarket modifications and oxidation, this specimen offers the linear power delivery and structural rigidity intended by Toyota's flagship performance division.",
